{
  "texts": [
    "Therefore, in our future study, we plan to compare the performances of a fine-tuning model using LoRA's adaptation approaches.",
    "Furthermore, there is a need for enhancement in the design of the interaction head.",
    "Currently, this component is composed of a sequence of straightforward FC layers, which exhibits reduced effectiveness in cold bindings.",
    "To address this, potential strategies include the integration of a squeezeand-excitation network [58], capsule network [59], crossattention [60], and other alternatives.",
    "ConclusionIn this study, we employed knowledge adaptation to efficiently and accurately predict binding probability."
  ]
}